    <description><![CDATA[
mdbub is a mindmap tool for your terminal. Fast. Fluid. Keyboard-native. Built for thinkers who live in the CLI.

## Features

- **Quick Mode**: Instant mini-editor for rapid note capture
- **Edit Mode**: Full-screen terminal interface for folding, searching, tagging
- **Keyboard-native UX**: Everything is hotkey driven. Customize to your liking
- **Zero-mouse flow**: It's not just fast. It feels alive under your fingertips

## Usage

```
mdbub quick    # Quick mode for rapid note capture
mdbub edit     # Full-screen editing mode
mdbub version  # Show version and build info
```
]]></description>
